requests_mock.get(
    'https://example.com/.well-known/webfinger?resource=acct:profile@example.com'
    , json={'links': [{'rel': 'profile', 'href':
    'https://profile.example.com/u/moo'}, {'rel': 'self', 'href':
    'https://profile.example.com/u/moo'}, {'rel': 'self', 'href':
    'https://self.example.com/u/moo'}, {'rel': 'posts', 'href':
    'https://example.com/u/moo/posts'}]})
assert webfinger.get_profiles('@profile@example.com') == {
    'https://profile.example.com/u/moo', 'https://self.example.com/u/moo'}
requests_mock.get(
    'https://example.com/.well-known/webfinger?resource=acct:empty@example.com'
    , json={'links': [{'rel': 'nothing', 'href':
    'https://profile.example.com/u/moo'}, {'rel': 'still-nothing', 'href':
    'https://self.example.com/u/moo'}, {'rel': 'posts', 'href':
    'https://example.com/u/moo/posts'}]})
assert webfinger.get_profiles('@empty@example.com') == set()
